These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, juice, sprite
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: scientific, musical, martial-arts, satire, animation, time-travel
 1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 2. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person drinking juice##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 7. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
12. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |    3     |  4   |       5       |   6   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | sprite | fanta    | cola | hot-chocolate | juice |
| Movie-Genre        | musical      | time-travel  | satire | scientific | animation          | martial-arts  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-2::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, juice, milk, mirinda, tea
The people use 6 different means of transport: boat, trike, van, subway, quad-bike, helicopter
 1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 3. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person driving the van##1
 7. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
 8. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
10. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the van##1
11. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
12. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
13. the person driving the van is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
14. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |       3       |    4     |     5     |    6     |
| Beverage      | coffee  | milk     | hot-chocolate | juice    | tea       | mirinda  |
| Transport   | helicopter | boat | van       | subway | trike | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: fanta, 7up, sprite, tea, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
The people use 6 different means of transport: airplane, bus, motorbike, quad-bike, snowmobile, train
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
7. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking sprite##2
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |      3      |     4     |    5     |     6     |
| Beverage         | tea | 7up | sprite | hot-chocolate | fanta  | iced-tea    |
| Transport   | train      | motorbike  | snowmobile  | bus       | airplane | quad-bike |

