.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-4::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  paramedic, lawyer, chef, architect, freelancer, dancer
The people have 6 different hobbies: camping, card-games, drawing, fishing, reading, writing
 1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the chef##1
 2. the freelancer is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is the architect##1
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the dancer##1
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the freelancer##3
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
 8. the dancer is between the person who's hobby is camping and the freelancer##2
 9. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the dancer##3
10. the paramedic is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5    |       6       |
| Job   | lawyer   | dancer     | freelancer | paramedic        | architect   | chef |
| Hobby      | camping | reading | drawing  | card-games | writing | fishing       |

