.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-5::.
There 6 different types of food: cabbage, cranberry, grapefruit, radish, strawberry, watermelon
6 different pets are kept: goat, fish, goldfish, ferret, bird, cat
1. the person eating grapefruit is between the person eating cabbage and the person eating strawberry##2
2. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
3. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
4. the owner of the cat is the person eating cranberry##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the goat is the person eating strawberry##1
7. the person eating radish is on the far right##1
8. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
9. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |     5     |    6     |
| Food          | watermelon | strawberry | grapefruit | cabbage | cranberry | radish   |
| Pet   | bird   | goat   | fish    | ferret | cat    | goldfish |

