.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-6::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, firefighter, lawyer, project-manager, scientist
There are 6 different nationalities: egyptian, american, argentine, german, pakistani, indonesian
 1. the german is on the left or right of the bartender##3
 2. the bartender is between the german and the scientist##2
 3. the pakistani is on the right of the german##1
 4. the pakistani is on the right of the firefighter##1
 5. the lawyer is on the left or right of the argentine##3
 6. the pakistani is on the far right##1
 7. the bartender is the indonesian##1
 8. the lawyer is on the left or right of the argentine##3
 9. the scientist is on the right of the american##1
10. the dancer is on the far left##1
11. the egyptian is on the left of the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |   2    |     3     |     4      |      5       |        6        |
| Job     | dancer        | lawyer | scientist | bartender  | firefighter  | project-manager |
| Nationality   | argentine | american   | egyptian  | indonesian | german | pakistani          |

