.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-7::.
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, goat, goldfish, guinea-pig, hedgehog
The people have 6 different hobbies: board-games, photography, cooking, chess, skydiving, traveling
 1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
 3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 9. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the owner of the goldfish##1
10. the owner of the goat is between the owner of the goldfish and the person who's hobby is photography##2
11. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |    3     |     4      |   5    |     6      |
| Pet         | hedgehog | goat      | goldfish | guinea-pig | ferret | chinchilla |
| Hobby   | photography  | board-games | skydiving   | traveling        | cooking   | chess |

