.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-8::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, juice, tea, water
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: iris, bellflower, daffodil, daisy, amaryllis, zinnia
 1. the person who growsamaryllis is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 3. the person who growsbellflower is the person drinking tea##1
 4. the person who growsiris is the person drinking juice##1
 5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 7. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 9. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the person who growsdaisy is the person drinking water##1
11. the person drinking tea is the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2     |   3   |    4     |    5    |     6      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | water     | juice | iced-tea | cola    | tea        |
| Flower      | daffodil   | daisy | iris | amaryllis   | zinnia | bellflower |

