6. the owner of the rabbit is the person eating potato##1
7. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person eating pear##1
8. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2     |      3      |   4    |     5     |       6       |
