.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-14::.
There 6 different types of food: banana, blueberry, broccoli, carrot, cherry, cucumber
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, davidoff, vegafina, pall-mall, siglo, bolivar
 1. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 2. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
 3. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 4. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3
 5. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person eating cherry is between the pall-mall-smoker and the davidoff-smoker##2
 8. the ritmeester-smoker is the person eating broccoli##1
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
10. the person eating banana is the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |    3     |     4     |     5      |   6    |
| Food        | banana  | cherry | cucumber | blueberry | broccoli   | carrot |
| Cigar   | davidoff | vegafina | pall-mall    | siglo     | ritmeester | bolivar    |

