3. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
5. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the subway##2
7. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person driving the quad-bike##1
8. the person driving the taxi is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
9. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |  3   |     4      |  5   |    6    |
| Hobby         | drawing  | collecting | rock-climbing  | skydiving     | sudoku | magic-tricks    |
| Transport   | quad-bike | subway     | taxi | skateboard | car  | jet-ski |

